Author Note:

This repository contains my personal synthesis and revision notes from my M.S.
coursework. It is shared for educational and portfolio purposes.

Please do not present this material as official university course material,
professor-authored content, or institutional documentation.

Original Author:
Ayushman Mishra

Work:
Robotics Concept Stack

Description:
A robotics-oriented knowledge stack distilled from M.S. coursework, covering
linear algebra, system dynamics and control, robot modeling, reinforcement
learning, robot perception, generative AI, applied machine learning,
multi-robot systems, mechatronics, and space robotics.

